            <title>[LUDOC-418] git link on http://wiki.lustre.org/Using_Gerrit not working</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-418</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://wiki.lustre.org/Using_Gerrit&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://wiki.lustre.org/Using_Gerrit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The git link doesn&apos;t work for me:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;$ git clone -b master &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;git://git.hpdd.intel.com/fs/lustre-release.git&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; lustre-master&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cloning into &apos;lustre-master&apos;...&lt;br/&gt;
fatal: unable to connect to git.hpdd.intel.com:&lt;br/&gt;
git.hpdd.intel.com&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0: 192.198.160.59&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;: errno=Connection refused&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Should it be?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;$ git clone &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/fs/lustre-release&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/fs/lustre-release&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

